    <thetext>Bibletime UI (as all other modern UI) should be able to auto-detect the system&apos;s language and, if the language is available, activate it automatically (whitout the user needing to get the file from the website m-a-n-u-a-l-l-y! :(

There should also be a place to manually change the UI language.

(really... how can such a great front end miss something so basic?! Not everyone is a computer expert)</thetext>
