You can take the pt_BR files as a basis. For br_BR translation file for versions 2.9 is located here:

  https://gitorious.org/bibletime/bibletime/blobs/stable-2.9/i18n/messages/bibletime_ui_pt_BR.ts

For older 2.8 versions its here:

  https://gitorious.org/bibletime/bibletime/blobs/stable-2.8/i18n/messages/bibletime_ui_pt_BR.ts

For the development branch:

  https://gitorious.org/bibletime/bibletime/blobs/master/i18n/messages/bibletime_ui_pt_BR.ts

